</comment>
                            <comment id="14073640" author="hudson" created="Thu, 24 Jul 2014 21:00:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SUCCESS: Integrated in HBase-1.0 #68 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-1.0/68/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-1.0/68/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
