&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14088407" author="stack" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 22:43:12 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;hbase.master.wait.on.regionservers.mintostart should be set to 1.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Does it have to be this way Jimmy?  This is in branch-1 too?  That&apos;d be a pain for users.  Would be ok for master I&apos;d say.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14089405" author="jxiang" created="Thu, 7 Aug 2014 16:28:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately, it is in branch-1 too. The problem is that master uses the same RPC port as a region server now. Not sure how to handle this better.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14127780" author="jxiang" created="Tue, 9 Sep 2014 23:33:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Release note is removed since we are going to change the code so that additional config is not needed. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11604&quot; title=&quot;Disable co-locating meta/master by default&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-11604&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-11604&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14330938" author="enis" created="Sat, 21 Feb 2015 23:32:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing this issue after 0.99.0 release. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
